{"tid":1630731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重中之重］香港人權與民主法案過後 爭取對香港實施全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法案","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:16:33.000Z","uid":62369,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd3fec5f42d81092c94eeb81ae6030184d63191","tid":1630731,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"香港人權與民主法案尚未通過的，所以有機會影響通過嘅事都希望大家忍一忍手先。<br />\n<br />\n待香港人權與民主法案通過之後 <br />\n向國際爭取對香港實施<strong>全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法案</strong><br />\n淨係美國唔夠嘅 最好所有文明國家一齊抵制港共中共<br />\n點樣可以成個警隊制裁？可以制裁到唔比佢地入境唔比佢地移民嗎？<br />\n大家一齊集思廣益"},{"pid":"8743780da8089da9719e40aafec161b2a6ba1859","tid":1630731,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1384d2438527a3d42ffed48fb9f8415bbc6835","tid":1630731,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"yes,仲有hk policy reevaluation act 可以用"},{"pid":"efa5f7649519a03de5438c8f405377f67413404b","tid":1630731,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【十八區裝修指南】</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/4/viewer?mid=18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO&amp;ll=22.37581035920343%2C114.11057920000007&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F4%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO%26ll%3D22.37581035920343%252C114.11057920000007%26z%3D11&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6mvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=61c71ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/4/viewer?mid=18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO&amp;ll=22.37581035920343%2C114.11057920000007&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">18區開花 裝修手足入嚟接Job</span></spa